@startuml
title Agent Worktree Switch via EnterWorktree — Before vs After

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #5C5470
  LifeLineBorderColor #5C5470
  ParticipantBorderColor #6C5CE7
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #1E1A2E
  ParticipantFontColor #E0DDE8
  ActorBackgroundColor #1E1A2E
  ActorBorderColor #6C5CE7
  ActorFontColor #E0DDE8
  GroupBorderColor #5C5470
  GroupHeaderFontColor #FAB387
  GroupBodyBackgroundColor #1E1A2E
  DividerBackgroundColor #313244
  DividerFontColor #FAB387
}

skinparam backgroundColor #0E0E1A
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #313244
skinparam noteBorderColor #5C5470
skinparam noteFontColor #E0DDE8

actor "Claude\n(agent)" as Claude #8839EF
participant "Interactive\nShell ($PWD)" as Shell
participant "Transcript\nJSONL" as JSONL
participant "Body.tsx\n(OSC 7 + agentCwdHint)" as Body
participant "Rust\ntranscript watcher" as Watcher
participant "useAgentStatus" as Status
participant "WorkspaceView\nbridge effect" as Workspace
participant "updatePaneCwd" as Update
participant "useGitBranch +\nuseGitWorktree" as GitHooks
participant "Header\n(tree chip + branch)" as Header

== BEFORE — OSC 7 + agentCwdHint only ==

Claude -> Claude : Invoke built-in tool\n**EnterWorktree({ path: "/.../worktrees/dummy" })**
note over Claude
  Tool runs **inside Claude Code's host process**.
  It mutates the **agent's** cwd, NOT the shell's.
  Nothing is written to the PTY stream.
end note

Claude -[#FF6B6B]x Shell : (no `cd`, no OSC 7)
Claude -[#FF6B6B]x Body : (no recognizable text\npattern in PTY output)

note over Body #443344
  Body.tsx receives some
  rendered summary text, but
  `Entering worktree(<name>)` /
  `Ran cd ...` patterns
  don't match. **No event fires.**
end note

note over Header #443344
  pane.cwd stays at the
  starting checkout.
  Branch chip + worktree chip
  point at the wrong worktree.
end note

== AFTER — same paths + new structured channel from JSONL ==

Claude -> Claude : Invoke built-in tool\n**EnterWorktree({ path: "/.../worktrees/dummy" })**

Claude -[#FF6B6B]x Shell : (still no `cd`, no OSC 7)
Claude -[#FF6B6B]x Body : (still no PTY text match)

Claude -[#10B981]> JSONL : write line with\n**top-level cwd = "/.../worktrees/dummy"**\n+ tool_use record

JSONL -[#10B981]> Watcher : tail line
Watcher -> Watcher : extract `cwd` field\nlast_cwd != observed?

alt cwd changed
  Watcher -[#10B981]> Status : **emit_agent_cwd**\n{ sessionId, cwd }
  Status -> Status : filter by ptyId,\ndedupe vs prev.cwd
  Status -[#10B981]> Workspace : agentStatus.cwd =\n"/.../worktrees/dummy"
  Workspace -> Workspace : guard: active session +\nrunning + cwd != pane.cwd
  Workspace -[#10B981]> Update : updatePaneCwd(\nsessionId, paneId, cwd)
  Update -[#10B981]> GitHooks : pane.cwd changes
  GitHooks -[#10B981]> Header : branch + worktree-name\nrefetch (~300 ms)

  note over Header #2D4A3E
    tree dummy
    | worktree-dummy
  end note
else cwd unchanged
  Watcher -[#FFC857]x Status : (no event — dedup)
end

@enduml
